      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit la fonction $V \\colon \\R^2 \\to \\R$ définie par $$V(r,\\theta) = \\dfrac{\\cos \\theta}{r^2}$$",
        "html": "<p>Soit la fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(V \\colon \\R^2 \\to\n\\R\\)</span> définie par <span class=\"math display\">\\[V(r,\\theta) =\n\\dfrac{\\cos \\theta}{r^2}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "605503bc-f689-4ad0-a57c-16e17056210a",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Donner l'ensemble de définition de $V$.",
        "html": "<p>Donner l’ensemble de définition de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(V\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7b7c5eec-478f-44c9-a909-1f742333aa5f",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\mathcal{D}_V = \\R^* \\times \\R$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{D}_V = \\R^* \\times\n\\R\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "10942570-2754-4f2f-8cd0-1786caa3f044",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer les dérivées partielles $\\dpa{V}{r}$ et $\\dpa{V}{\\theta}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer les dérivées partielles <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpa{V}{r}\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpa{V}{\\theta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0373f81d-8848-4029-b978-781328330628",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "pour $(r,\\theta) \\in \\mathcal{D}_V$, on a \n\t\t\t\\[ \\dpa{V}{r} = -\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta, \\ \\ \\dpa{V}{\\theta} = -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\]",
        "html": "<p>pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\((r,\\theta) \\in\n\\mathcal{D}_V\\)</span>, on a <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\dpa{V}{r} =\n-\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta, \\ \\ \\dpa{V}{\\theta} =\n-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5860b1a5-d883-4530-9f34-8a61927d870a",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer les dérivées partielles secondes $\\dpsp{V}{r}$, $\\dpa{V}{\\theta}$ et $\\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer les dérivées partielles secondes <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpsp{V}{r}\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpa{V}{\\theta}\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a20d87ba-666b-4e9f-9603-cd3d266b5c70",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "pour $(r,\\theta) \\in \\mathcal{D}_V$, on a\n\t\t\t$$\\begin{align*} \n\t\t\t\\dpsp{V}{r} &= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[ -\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta \\right] = \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n\t\t\t\\dpsp{V}{\\theta} &= \\dpa{}{\\theta}\\left[ -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n\t\t\t\\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta} &= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[ -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = \\frac{2}{r^3}\\sin\\theta\n\t\t\t\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p>pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\((r,\\theta) \\in\n\\mathcal{D}_V\\)</span>, on a <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n            \\dpsp{V}{r} &amp;= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[ -\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta\n\\right] = \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n            \\dpsp{V}{\\theta} &amp;= \\dpa{}{\\theta}\\left[\n-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = -\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta \\\\\n            \\dpsm{V}{r}{\\theta} &amp;= \\dpa{}{r}\\left[\n-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta \\right] = \\frac{2}{r^3}\\sin\\theta\n            \\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4f7f1d02-3714-4aa5-a26e-dd28ee0582b6",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En déduire que $$\\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r} \\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r} \\right]  + \\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]  = 0.$$",
        "html": "<p>En déduire que <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r}\n\\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r} \\right]  + \\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta\n\\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]  = 0.\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b6beb7e4-1f50-42c3-85a7-588ccc4fd31a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On a\n\t\t\t\\begin{eqnarray*}\n\t\t\t\t\\lefteqn{\\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r} \\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r} \\right]  + \\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]} \\\\\n\t\t\t\t&=& \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r \\dpa{V}{r} + r^2 \\dpsp{V}{r} \\right] + \\left[ \\cos\\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} + \\sin\\theta \\dpsp{V}{\\theta} \\right] \\\\\n\t\t\t\t&=& \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r (-\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta) + r^2 \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\right] + \\left[ \\cos\\theta (-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta) + \\sin\\theta (-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta) \\right] \\\\\n\t\t\t\t&=& \\frac{\\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta}{r^2}(-4+ 6-1-1) \\\\\n\t\t\t\t&=& 0\n\t\t\\end{eqnarray*}",
        "html": "<p>On a <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n                \\lefteqn{\\sin \\theta \\ \\dpa{}{r} \\left[ r^2 \\dpa{V}{r}\n\\right]  + \\dpa{}{\\theta} \\left[ \\sin \\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} \\right]} \\\\\n                &amp;=&amp; \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r \\dpa{V}{r} + r^2\n\\dpsp{V}{r} \\right] + \\left[ \\cos\\theta \\dpa{V}{\\theta} + \\sin\\theta\n\\dpsp{V}{\\theta} \\right] \\\\\n                &amp;=&amp; \\sin\\theta \\left[ 2r\n(-\\frac{2}{r^3}\\cos\\theta) + r^2 \\frac{6}{r^4}\\cos\\theta \\right] +\n\\left[ \\cos\\theta (-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\sin\\theta) + \\sin\\theta\n(-\\frac{1}{r^2}\\cos\\theta) \\right] \\\\\n                &amp;=&amp; \\frac{\\cos\\theta\\sin\\theta}{r^2}(-4+ 6-1-1)\n\\\\\n                &amp;=&amp; 0\n        \n\\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
}